<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="strcoll" id="strcoll">strcoll</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>

文法:

</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cstring&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">int</span> <span class="kw3">strcoll</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">const</span> <span class="kw4">char</span> <span class="sy2">*</span>文字列<span class="nu0">1</span>, <span class="kw4">const</span> <span class="kw4">char</span> <span class="sy2">*</span>文字列<span class="nu0">2</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>
strcoll関数は<a href="strcmp" class="wikilink1" title="jp:string:c:strcmp">strcmp</a>と同じように<code>文字列1</code>と<code>文字列2</code>を比較しますが、strcollは<a href="../../../c/date/setlocale" class="wikilink1" title="c:date:setlocale">setlocale</a>関数で設定されたロケール情報も使用して比較を行います。
</p>

<p>
関連トピック: <a href="../../c/date/setlocale" class="wikilink1" title="jp:c:date:setlocale">setlocale</a>, <a href="strcmp" class="wikilink1" title="jp:string:c:strcmp">strcmp</a>, <a href="strxfrm" class="wikilink1" title="jp:string:c:strxfrm">strxfrm</a>
</p>

